org.gbif.api.vocabulary

Enum TranslationLanguage

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TranslationLanguage>
      • org.gbif.api.vocabulary.TranslationLanguage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TranslationLanguage>

    public enum TranslationLanguage
extends Enum<TranslationLanguage>
    Enumeration for all the translation languages that we use in Crowdin.

    It stores the locale, the ISO_639_1 and ISO_639_3 codes, and the name of the language in English.

    See Also:
    Crowdin languages
